ðŸ”‘ Authentication

Request: Login (JWT)

Method: POST

URL: {{base_url}}/token/

Body (raw JSON):

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}


Test Script (to auto-save token):

pm.environment.set("access_token", pm.response.json().access);

ðŸ’¬ Conversations

Request: Create Conversation

Method: POST

URL: {{base_url}}/conversations/

Headers:

Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json


Body (raw JSON):

{
  "participants": [1, 2]
}


Request: List Conversations

Method: GET

URL: {{base_url}}/conversations/

Headers:

Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

ðŸ“© Messages

Request: Send Message

Method: POST

URL: {{base_url}}/messages/

Headers:

Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json


Body (raw JSON):

{
  "conversation": 1,
  "content": "Hello there!"
}


Request: List Messages (paginated)

Method: GET

URL: {{base_url}}/messages/?page=1

Headers:

Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


Request: Filter Messages (by sender + date)

Method: GET

URL:

{{base_url}}/messages/?sender=john&start_date=2025-01-01T00:00:00Z&end_date=2025-01-31T23:59:59Z


Headers:

Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

ðŸ”’ Unauthorized Access Test

Request: Access Conversations without Token

Method: GET

URL: {{base_url}}/conversations/

No Authorization header

Expected:

{
  "detail": "Authentication credentials were not provided."
}

